<tr bgcolor="yellow"><td width=50% border=0 valign="top">(hari Ahad 10 April, 2011) Sekurang-kurangnya enam orang terbunuh dan 11 lagi cedera semalam apabila seorang lelaki bersenjata melepaskan tembakan rambang di sebuah pusat beli-belah yang penuh sesak di Alphen aan den Rijn, kira-kira 25 kilometer ke barat daya Amsterdam, sebelum menembak dirinya sendiri.</td>
<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">(Sunday 10 April 2011) At least six people were killed and 11 others wounded yesterday when an armed man started shooting people at random in a crowded shopping mall in Alphen aan den Rijn, about 25km south-west of Amsterdam, before shooting himself.
</td></tr>

