<tr bgcolor="yellow"><td width=50% border=0 valign="top">(hari Isnin 28 Mac, 2011) Seorang ahli parlimen Indonesia, Roy Suryo dihalau keluar dari kapal terbang Lion Air hari ini kerana mengambil tempat duduk yang ditempah oleh dua penumpang lain untuk dirinya serta isterinya.  Tiket Roy dan isteri menunjukkan mereka sepatutnya menaiki penerbangan yang seterusnya pada pukul 7.45 pagi tetapi mereka berkeras mahu kekal duduk di dalam kapal terbang yang akan berlepas pada pukul 6.15 pagi.</td>
<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">A member of the Indonesian Parliament, Roy Suryo was driven out of the Lion Air plane today for occupying the seats that had been booked by two other passengers for himself and his wife.  The ticket for Roy and his wife showed that they should have boarded the next flight at 7.45 but they insisted on remaining in their seats in the plane which was taking off at 6.15 in the morning.
</td></tr>

