<tr bgcolor="yellow"><td width=50% border=0 valign="top">(hari Ahad, 27 Mac 2011)  Sekurang-kurangnya 2,000 wanita sudah memohon untuk bertemu dengan jutawan Australia berusia 80 tahun yang mahu mencari isteri di kalangan wanita Korea, kata agensi pencari jodoh, UVIS, kelmarin.  Firma itu berkata, selepas kematian isterinya tujuh tahun lalu, duda itu jatuh cinta dengan Korea berikutan kekerapan beliau melawat negara itu atas urusan perniagaan.</td>
<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">At least 2,000 women have applied to meet an 80-year-old Australian millionaire who wants to seek a wife among Korean women, said matchmaking agency UVIS yesterday.  The firm said that after the death of his wife seven years ago, the widower fell in love with Korea following his repeated visits to the country on business matters.
</td></tr>

<tr><td colspan=2 border=0><font color=red><b>Vocabulary from the above sentence(s):</b></font>

