<tr bgcolor="yellow"><td width=50% border=0 valign="top">(hari Rabu, 23 Mac 2011)  Presiden Bolivia, Evo Morales menggesa anugerah Nobel Keamanan Presiden Amerika Syarikat, Barack Obama ditarik balik kerana menyifatkan keputusan pemimpin itu melancarkan serangan tentera terhadap Libya menunjukkan beliau tidak layak mendapat anugerah itu.  "Dua tahun lalu, kita mendengar bahawa Presiden Obama memenangi anugerah Nobel Keamanan tetapi adakah beliau mempertahankan keamanan dunia sekarang, atau tidakkah beliau yang mencetuskan keganasan?" kata Morales kepada pemberita.</td>
<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">The President of Bolivia, Evo Morales has urged that the Nobel Peace award to the United States' President Barack Obama be withdrawn describing the leader's decision in launching a military attack on Libya as showing that he is not qualified to receive the award.  "Two years ago we heard that President Obama won the Nobel Peace award but has he defended world peace today or isn't he the one to have sparked off violence?" he told reporters.
</td></tr>

