<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">Yahoo Inc. once again will cut down on the total number of its workers in 6 weeks' time while its rival Google Inc. prepares to increase the number of its staff to a record high this year, at the same time showing the different directions in which the two internet giants are taking.</td></tr>
