<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">Although they know that they can earn more by prostituting in a 5-star hotel yet a group of Indonesian-national prostitutes are willing to seek customers in massage parlours for as little as RM40 so as to avoid being arrested for entering the country illegally.</td></tr>
