<tr border=0 bgcolor="yellow"  bordercolor="white"><td width=50% border=0 valign="top">(24-11-10) Kebanyakan rakyat Britain mahu Putera William dan tunangnya, Kate Middleton menjadi raja dan permaisuri yang akan datang, dan bukan pewaris takhta sekarang, Putera Charles dan isterinya, Camilla.  Tiga tinjauan pendapat umum yang disiarkan hari ini menunjukkan gelombang sokongan padu terhadap William selepas anak lelaki sulung Charles dengan mendiang bekas isterinya, Putera Diana itu mengumumkan beliau dan Kate akan berkahwin pada tahun depan.</td>
<td width=50% border=0 valign="top">The majority of British citizens want Prince William and his fiancee Kate Middleton to become the future King and Queen and not the present inheritor to the throne, Prince Charles and his wife Camilla.  Three surveys of public opinion published today showed a wave of solid support towards William after the eldest son of Charles with his late ex-wife Princess Diana announced that he and Kate are going to get married next year.</td></tr>
